A massive industrial assembly line in a sleek factory, where streams of glowing code symbols flow through transparent pipes and precision robotic arms with magnifying lenses inspect and repair tiny floating Java class icons, removing red warning symbols and replacing them with green checkmarks. The scene is bathed in warm amber light from overhead industrial lamps, with steam rising from polished brass machinery. In the foreground, a complex mechanical sieve catches and filters out bug-shaped particles while clean, organized code blocks emerge on a conveyor belt heading toward a pristine glass container. The aesthetic blends Victorian-era industrial revolution machinery with modern technological precision, featuring copper gears, analog gauges, and holographic quality metrics floating above workstations. Studio Ghibli style with intricate mechanical details, soft lighting, and a sense of wonder at the craftsmanship of maintaining perfect code quality at scale.
